50|$|SciFri {{was created}} when the National Science Foundation agreed {{to fund a}} weekly science talk-show on NPR. After the Gulf War in 1991, NPR created the daily talk show Talk of the Nation, and {{incorporated}} <b>Science</b> <b>Friday</b> into it. <b>Science</b> <b>Friday</b> moved <b>from</b> <b>NPR</b> to Public Radio International in 2014.|$|R
